# Third-Party Vendored Code

## companion/

The entire `companion/` directory (the Factorio mod `claude-interface`, the
Python bridge, the server/run scripts, configs, and relay) was vendored from:

    https://github.com/QRY91/claude-in-factorio
    at commit 55c6020 ("feat: supervisor orchestration + desync-safe character
    lookups", 2026-02-23), the latest upstream commit at vendoring time.

It is included here under its original license, retained at
`companion/LICENSE`. Copyright remains with the original author (QRY91) for the
vendored portions; subsequent modifications in this repository are made by this
project's authors.

This code was vendored (rather than kept as a separate dependency) to unify the
factorioctl CLI/MCP server and its companion bridge into a single repository
with one build, test, and review pipeline. Upstream was inactive at the time of
vendoring.
